sellerCard.oneLiner: We are Website development and Digital Marketing service provider
sellerCard.description:
Hi, thank you for visiting our profile. We have provided Website/Software development and Business development services since 2009. We have extensive experience with Laravel, WordPress, JavaScript, NodeJS, ReactJS, PHP, MySql, Bootstrap, AJAX, GIT, Photoshop, SEO, Social Media Marketing, and Digital Marketing. As a creative agency, we built various business and applications like document management systems, SaaS, AI, CRM, ERP, PHP Framework, financial websites, e-commerce websites, Wedding websites, Charity websites, etc. 

Our core objective is, "Honest, Friendly and Easy to Work with".

description.content:
Hi,

I am Shakil Ahsan, The Seller with all positive reviews. I have the expertise to precisely fit your business needs. Quality is my top priority, I work closely with you to ensure that your website not only meets but exceeds your expectations, helping you achieve your business goals. I am working as a professional Web Developer since 2009.


SERVICES I OFFER:


  • AI-driven software development
  • SaaS applications
  • E-commerce web applications
  • Management Software
  • Custom website development (frontend and backend)
  • Website creation from scratch
  • Development in PHP Laravel, Vue js Single Page Application
  • Frontend web development
  • Figma to HTML, XD to HTML conversion
  • Database architecture (MySQL, MongoDB, Redis)
  • Server management (Azure, AWS, VPS/Linux, Digital Owsen)
  • Deployments
  • Domain and Hosting Setup


YOU CAN EXPECT FROM ME: 


  • Dedicated Support with Regular updates
  • Stress-free development experience
  • One month of FREE post-development support
  • Successful project delivery
  • 100% satisfaction guaranteed with fast and responsive communication


Please message me before placing an order, because cancellation of the order will affect my performance.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you make a responsive design for my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes of-course, You will get 100% bug free, all browser supported, and all device screen supported responsive website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is my website will be secure?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes of-course, your website will be secured and malware protected. 

You will have:
  
  -- Authentication System
  -- Vulnerabilities From CSRF (Cross Site Request Forgery)
  -- Protection against Cross Site Scripting.
  -- SQL Injection

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you upload content to my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes of-course, if you provide me content then, I can update them to your website. If you don't have content then I can upload demo content for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Which service is best for host Laravel application? VPS, dedicated or Sheared Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To host laravel application into VPS or a dedicated server is a better option. Cpanel can also be used to host Laravel, but it requires some changes in core code as Laravel is not built to be hosted on a shared hosting like Cpanel.
